      "text": "Done. The branch is committed locally. To push and open a PR:\n\n```bash\ncd ~/agentsong\ngit push -u origin feat/cursor-cline-aider-readers\n```\n\nThen open a PR from `feat/cursor-cline-aider-readers` → `master`.\n\n**PR title suggestion:**\n```\nfeat(readers): add Cursor, Cline, and Aider readers (9 readers total)\n```\n\n**What the PR contains:**\n- `readers/cursor.py` — SQLite key-value store reader (10 tests)\n- `readers/cline.py` — JSON file reader (9 tests)\n- `readers/aider.py` — Markdown log reader (10 tests)\n- ADR-011 (naming change agenson → AgentSON)\n- Updated CLI with cursor/cline/aider support\n- 50/51 tests passing\n\n**What it means for AgentSON:**\n- 6 readers → **9 readers**\n- Covers **Tier 1 (Cursor)** and **Tier 2 (Cline, Aider)**\n- AgentLog has 2 working readers. You have 9.",
      "timestamp": 1783288286331
